        <abstract> 
<p>Has received CD’s letter [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">12050</hi>]. Gives CD the history of the Baly Medal and names previous recipients. It is not necessary for CD to be present for the award, but if he chooses to attend, arrangements could be made for him to arrive just before the presentation. CD will not be required to make an acceptance speech.</p> 
